01:04:40,280 --> 01:04:45,440
Saudações a Shri Guru, que é Shri Brahmadeva,

818
01:04:45,840 --> 01:04:49,600
Shri Vishnu e Shri Shiva e

819
01:04:50,000 --> 01:04:53,360
